{"tid":2383492,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜台南老家遭竊！清潔人員偷「珍貴簽名照」上網兜售","createTime":"2021-01-28T02:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T06:29:47.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"826e2809539cad4eca8f7c8b1a58c2ddde5779af","tid":2383492,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:51:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/01/28/1/11386672.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F01%2F28%2F1%2F11386672.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=f769445f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n子瑜今天驚傳台灣住家遭竊，據悉周子瑜的家人日前透過友人介紹找來清潔人員打掃家，豈料清潔人員卻連續2次偷走周子瑜的珍貴簽名照、海報、專輯等；周子瑜家人察覺後趕緊報案，高雄市刑大3天前逮捕涉案汪姓女清潔員並扣得不少贓物，至於是否已全數追回待進一步釐清。"},{"pid":"3289c4e1cd9a8090a08396960681abd17c851e51","tid":2383492,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:51:17.000Z","msg":"警方當場查扣周子瑜簽名的個人照62張，周子瑜或所有TWICE團圓簽名的專輯11套、TWICE寫真書2本，不過有1套專輯已被依3000元賣出；汪女坦承犯行，供稱認為轉賣、有利可圖才行竊，警方將她依竊盜罪嫌移送台南地檢署，獲2萬元交保。"},{"pid":"9bf1531bee6bb059cbc9c950a716c845cc73ffb8","tid":2383492,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:51:31.000Z","msg":"據了解，簽名照是周子瑜家人自行印出，由周子瑜簽名，其他專輯及寫真書則由家人收藏，而竊賊將商品放上蝦皮網站，5張簽名照1組賣250元、1套專輯3000元，甚至簽名的寫真書賣1萬元高價。"},{"pid":"20a1b4213effc1855c5a429ba7deffbfa3932a82","tid":2383492,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/01/28/1/11385838.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F01%2F28%2F1%2F11385838.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%2